{"tid":1083071,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳6月利物浦元老隊訪港vs多蒙特 艾格 古積特 真高拿獻技","createTime":"2019-03-29T11:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T12:42:36.000Z","uid":7828,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bc77cfb3519da8166d4264a8a133b4c8b3bf390a","tid":1083071,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T11:02:59.000Z","msg":"今夏利物浦及多蒙特訪港！說的是兩軍元老隊，有傳將於6月7日來港踢一場友誼賽，地點是香港大球場，而且賽事會大搞，有傳紅軍名單包括丹尼爾艾格、古積特、艾德列治、貝加、門將杜迪克、韋斯特維特，如果「神奇隊長」謝拉特的檔期適合，亦有機會來港。<br />\n<br />\n至於多蒙特元老隊，就有前鋒真高拿、列度、前隊長基爾、維丹費拿，以及奧禾莫耶拉等，詳細名單仍待大會落實。多利名宿戰其實近年不時上演，包括在多蒙特主場及泰國舉行。<br />\n<br />\n上周紅軍元老隊在晏菲路大戰AC米蘭，謝拉特殺入絕殺球贏3:2，亦令球迷津津樂道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190329/59427083\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190329%2F59427083&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7eoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=f2c916dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190329%2F59427083&h=3c7cf23e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190329/59427083</a>"},{"pid":"83428839e7b9f96641c7f9b19408b71c9fcd922f","tid":1083071,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T11:28:33.000Z","msg":"不知名球員"},{"pid":"aec5697abf309ea1ce9d6e5a53e818c9f0930fc2","tid":1083071,"uid":17832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T11:35:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86c5e25f5f8dd46d034e9e8f13bbbbf025cfe66a","tid":1083071,"uid":161731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:42:36.000Z","msg":"會唔會即場表演跣腳先"}]}